{"tid":2224314,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"營養學家？poly 碩士課程","createTime":"2020-09-30T12:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T06:37:20.000Z","uid":292107,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"585e5311780c9f3c24d94c9bc5bbd9bec36af4c8","tid":2224314,"uid":292107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"有冇朋友係完全冇經驗，但之後讀下diploma,入到營養相關的學位，今年poly有開營養與健康活齡學碩士學位。（今年開）學校建議要讀左呢d先。<br />\n<br />\napplicants without background on related disciplines are advised to take some nutrition courses <br />\n <br />\nPart-time programmes in HKUSPACE (at least three certificates including 1, 5 plus any one of 2, 3, 4)<br />\n <br />\n1. Advanced Certificate in Nutrition (4 Months)<br />\n2. Advanced Certificate in Child and Adolescent Nutrition (4 Months)<br />\n3. Advanced Certificate in Sport and Exercise Nutrition (5 Months)<br />\n4. Advanced Diploma in Sport and Exercise Nutrition (10 Months)<br />\n5. Advanced Certificate in Clinical Nutrition and Health Promotion (4 Months)"},{"pid":"95f1b3c83a0db52afeee70db5186f3f685d76db5","tid":2224314,"uid":11876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"小心讀完無工開<br />\n香港暫時得hku space個course讀完有得做deititian"},{"pid":"66053e1fb5bc0e5ba4241e938eb858653ea89475","tid":2224314,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"讀完做康X來<br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n注冊營養師係完全唔會關你事"},{"pid":"ce6db074766ae4a23b5e96548cfd081454b33559","tid":2224314,"uid":292107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95f1b3c83a0db52afeee70db5186f3f685d76db5","tid":2224314,"uid":11876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"小心讀完無工開<br />\n香港暫時得hku space個course讀完有得做deititian"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"我都知呀，post grad 果個，不過而家都冇咩市場，即使reg左"},{"pid":"70f7017a459f5bcd1ecb45c2297e5310dfa41cf1","tid":2224314,"uid":292107,"like":0,"di